      <QUOTE REND=blockquote><LG type=couplet><L>Poor Adam and Eve were from Eden turned out, 
           <L>As a punishment due to their sin; 
        <L>But here after <num value="8">eight</num>, if you loiter about, 
           <L>As a punishment you'll be locked in.</QUOTE>

