        <QUOTE REND=blockquote><CIT><QUOTE>It will not be long ere we shall be at Tottenham High Cross; and when we come thither, I will make you some requital of your pains.</QUOTE><BIBL>--Izaak   Walton.</BIBL></CIT></QUOTE>

